genresAdvancedInfo.name: iowa indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Iowa indie music is characterized by its DIY ethos and raw, unpolished sound. Drawing inspiration from the state's rich musical history, Iowa indie bands create music that is both nostalgic and forward-thinking, blending elements of rock, folk, and punk to create a sound that is uniquely their own.
